    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about stepping away from the laptop though. the exhaustion isn't just physical. it feels like i'm just existing in this state of constant failure and i can't see a way to ever actually feel peace again. like no matter how much i sleep or how many breaks i take, the weight is still there. i just want the noise to stop. i just want everything to be quiet.",
